highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Me Porto Bonito” is the highest at #3.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 288 weeks straight.
“Do I Wanna Know?” by Arctic Monkeys is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 35 spots at #123.
“Bad Decisions (with BTS & Snoop Dogg)” by benny blanco, BTS, and Snoop Dogg is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #15.
